des: "I came up with this recipe after making pumpkin puree and seeing the container of peanut butter on my counter. With the yogurt and milk added, it's a creamy thick shake. For a thinner shake, add more milk or ice for a frosty shake."
ins: Blend milk, pumpkin puree, Greek yogurt, peanut butter, and pumpkin pie spice together in a blender until smooth.
